1
00:00:36,691 --> 00:00:39,089
=Love Behind the Mask=

2
00:00:39,712 --> 00:00:41,120
=Episode 8=

3
00:01:11,959 --> 00:01:12,840
You killed him?

4
00:01:15,439 --> 00:01:16,799
He slandered Your Highness.

5
00:01:18,400 --> 00:01:20,560
I just wanted
to teach him a lesson for you.

6
00:01:21,760 --> 00:01:23,079
It turned out to be a mishap.

7
00:01:24,560 --> 00:01:25,760
A mishap?

8
00:01:28,280 --> 00:01:29,400
Don't you believe me?

9
00:01:35,359 --> 00:01:36,120
Your Highness.

10
00:01:36,959 --> 00:01:37,599
Your Highness,

11
00:01:38,239 --> 00:01:39,079
how could you...

12
00:01:39,920 --> 00:01:41,519
He was trusted by His Majesty.

13
00:01:41,799 --> 00:01:42,519
Tonight,

14
00:01:42,879 --> 00:01:44,359
you didn't see anything.

15
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:46,439
Your Highness.

16
00:01:46,840 --> 00:01:49,040
Qiya was executed for dishonoring me.

17
00:01:49,959 --> 00:01:51,560
And I had a miscarriage due to anger.

18
00:01:52,760 --> 00:01:53,560
Right?

19
00:01:56,680 --> 00:01:57,079
Yes.

20
00:01:57,359 --> 00:01:58,000
That's right.

21
00:02:02,079 --> 00:02:02,799
Let's go.

22
00:02:12,319 --> 00:02:13,319
For Qiya's death,

23
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:15,840
I need a reasonable explanation.

24
00:02:16,199 --> 00:02:17,879
If I say it was a mishap,

25
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:19,319
will you believe me?

26
00:02:20,039 --> 00:02:21,199
The wound on his body

27
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:23,520
couldn't have been caused by a mishap.

28
00:02:24,639 --> 00:02:25,960
He killed my whole family.

29
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:29,479
He didn't even spare the children.

30
00:02:34,599 --> 00:02:35,400
Your Highness,

31
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:38,360
will you also feel sad

32
00:02:38,639 --> 00:02:39,639
for us lowly people?

33
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:47,120
So you chose to stay by my side

34
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:50,240
to find an opportunity for revenge?

35
00:02:54,159 --> 00:02:56,039
If you hadn't seized me,

36
00:02:57,159 --> 00:02:58,800
how would I have had the chance?

37
00:03:00,724 --> 00:03:02,599
♪Holding tightly to the obsession♪

38
00:03:02,599 --> 00:03:04,319
I remember when we first met,

39
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:06,400
you wanted to kill me.

40
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:08,199
What about now?

41
00:03:09,199 --> 00:03:10,719
Is it still the same?

42
00:03:11,439 --> 00:03:12,759
If I say yes,

43
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:14,879
what will you do?

44
00:03:15,060 --> 00:03:17,429
♪Isolated and cold♪

45
00:03:18,159 --> 00:03:19,479
This is nothing more

46
00:03:19,759 --> 00:03:21,879
than a slight difficulty

47
00:03:21,960 --> 00:03:23,919
while taming you.

48
00:03:24,479 --> 00:03:25,479
I want you

49
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:26,879
to submit

50
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:30,520
to me wholeheartedly.

51
00:03:30,624 --> 00:03:33,536
♪Even if the chaotic world
is like stardust♪

52
00:03:34,067 --> 00:03:36,590
♪Residing between your brows and eyes♪

53
00:03:37,602 --> 00:03:40,639
♪Suddenly a drop of regret is lifted♪

54
00:03:40,639 --> 00:03:41,879
Join me at the palace tomorrow.

55
00:03:42,080 --> 00:03:42,960
Obey me

56
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:44,280
if you want to live.

57
00:03:44,661 --> 00:03:47,712
♪Even if I can't express half of you♪

58
00:03:48,192 --> 00:03:50,602
♪Holding a falling petal♪

59
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:54,039
Father,

60
00:03:55,199 --> 00:03:57,000
Qiya not only harassed me when drunk,

61
00:03:57,639 --> 00:03:59,319
but also pushed me too hard

62
00:03:59,879 --> 00:04:00,919
and led to my miscarriage.

63
00:04:01,520 --> 00:04:03,199
Physician Sun can testify.

64
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:05,080
Father,

65
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:08,800
that was your unborn grandchild.

66
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:10,240
Physician Sun,

67
00:04:11,360 --> 00:04:12,479
is it true?

68
00:04:18,439 --> 00:04:19,240
Yes.

69
00:04:25,079 --> 00:04:25,920
Alright.

70
00:04:26,839 --> 00:04:28,040
The rest may leave first.

71
00:04:29,199 --> 00:04:31,399
I want to speak with him alone.

72
00:04:32,279 --> 00:04:33,120
Yes.

73
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:53,199
How exactly did Qiya die?

74
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:55,439
He was one of the best martial artists

75
00:04:55,759 --> 00:04:57,120
by my side.

76
00:04:57,720 --> 00:04:59,199
To protect Her Highness,

77
00:04:59,959 --> 00:05:00,720
I

78
00:05:01,920 --> 00:05:03,800
had to kill him no matter what.

79
00:05:05,199 --> 00:05:06,199
If not for you

80
00:05:06,480 --> 00:05:08,199
making my daughter happy,

81
00:05:08,639 --> 00:05:10,199
I would've killed you long ago.

82
00:05:10,639 --> 00:05:11,439
Remember,

83
00:05:12,040 --> 00:05:13,800
besides making her happy,

84
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:17,040
you better not have
any other intentions.

85
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:19,639
Understood.

86
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:38,160
Your Majesty,

87
00:05:38,560 --> 00:05:40,160
I went to Yeting to get my punishment.

88
00:05:40,399 --> 00:05:41,519
I won't make mistakes again.

89
00:05:41,879 --> 00:05:43,199
Lately, your performance

90
00:05:43,759 --> 00:05:44,959
has become more and more lax.

91
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:46,600
Do you

92
00:05:47,199 --> 00:05:49,279
not care
about your sister's life anymore?

93
00:05:49,959 --> 00:05:50,720
I wouldn't dare.

94
00:05:50,879 --> 00:05:52,560
I will devote myself to Your Majesty.

95
00:05:59,120 --> 00:06:01,639
Come and take a look.

96
00:06:02,879 --> 00:06:04,199
(Western Market)
Take a look.

97
00:06:05,716 --> 00:06:06,895
Here you go.

98
00:06:08,096 --> 00:06:10,307
Come and take a look.

99
00:06:12,115 --> 00:06:13,850
Come and have a look.

100
00:06:17,779 --> 00:06:19,833
Come and have a look.

101
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:34,879
Father.

102
00:06:36,399 --> 00:06:37,920
Is there any other movement

103
00:06:38,120 --> 00:06:39,079
in Zishang State?

104
00:06:39,279 --> 00:06:40,079
Father,

105
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:43,199
since the former Lord of Zishang
was executed for treason,

106
00:06:43,879 --> 00:06:45,279
Si Sheng, the new Lord of Zishang,

107
00:06:45,360 --> 00:06:46,800
has been very obedient.

108
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:48,920
He voluntarily
handed over military power

109
00:06:49,199 --> 00:06:50,959
and paid double tribute.

110
00:06:52,079 --> 00:06:53,120
Zishang State

111
00:06:53,279 --> 00:06:55,199
occupies a strategic point in Linzhao.

112
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:56,519
We must have total control

113
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:57,560
of it.

114
00:06:58,360 --> 00:06:59,519
I thought

115
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:01,399
that given the massacre
of Zishang State,

116
00:07:01,639 --> 00:07:02,560
other states

117
00:07:02,759 --> 00:07:04,079
dared not stir trouble again.

118
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:05,560
I didn't expect

119
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:07,759
that they secretly raised soldiers

120
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:08,680
and didn't pay tribute

121
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:10,240
to provoke my anger.

122
00:07:10,639 --> 00:07:11,279
Father,

123
00:07:11,759 --> 00:07:12,920
