124
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:16,160
It's hard for our first emperor
to unite the nation.

125
00:07:16,680 --> 00:07:17,360
After all,

126
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:19,639
our first emperor was a woman.

127
00:07:20,480 --> 00:07:21,920
With the benevolence of a woman,

128
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:23,759
she allowed

129
00:07:23,879 --> 00:07:25,120
the vassal lords

130
00:07:25,639 --> 00:07:27,000
to pass down the titles.

131
00:07:27,879 --> 00:07:28,920
Off our borders, Xuanhuang

132
00:07:29,240 --> 00:07:30,639
warred against us with all excuses.

133
00:07:31,240 --> 00:07:32,920
Let's solve external problems first,

134
00:07:33,560 --> 00:07:34,480
and then internal ones.

135
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:36,439
Father,

136
00:07:37,399 --> 00:07:38,360
Linzhao is now low

137
00:07:38,560 --> 00:07:39,519
on national wealth,

138
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:41,279
while Xuanhuang is powerful.

139
00:07:41,959 --> 00:07:42,680
I'm afraid the war

140
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:44,519
won't be in our favor.

141
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:45,920
Our neighbor Zhuyan

142
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:48,120
is financially strong.

143
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:49,839
Linzhao is now in trouble.

144
00:07:50,639 --> 00:07:52,079
And they'll be the next.

145
00:07:52,920 --> 00:07:54,360
All over the country,

146
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:56,560
everyone is in peril.

147
00:07:58,319 --> 00:07:59,240
I suppose

148
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:01,399
a negotiation

149
00:08:01,639 --> 00:08:02,199
is achievable.

150
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:04,120
I'm willing to go to Zhuyan

151
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:05,560
to lobby its emperor.

152
00:08:06,160 --> 00:08:06,959
Good.

153
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:09,680
You handled the matter

154
00:08:10,639 --> 00:08:11,920
of Zishang State well.

155
00:08:13,240 --> 00:08:14,040
Don't

156
00:08:14,560 --> 00:08:16,120
let me down on this task.

157
00:08:16,519 --> 00:08:17,839
If you need more manpower,

158
00:08:18,160 --> 00:08:19,360
you can decide on your own.

159
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:20,639
Set out immediately.

160
00:08:21,160 --> 00:08:22,000
Yes.

161
00:08:23,199 --> 00:08:23,959
Wait.

162
00:08:25,959 --> 00:08:27,720
When heading to Zhuyan,

163
00:08:28,199 --> 00:08:30,319
you must pass through Zishang State

164
00:08:30,639 --> 00:08:31,680
to take a look.

165
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:33,159
If Si Sheng is not fit

166
00:08:33,440 --> 00:08:34,840
to be the lord of a state,

167
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:37,399
I will strip him of his position.

168
00:08:38,279 --> 00:08:39,240
By then,

169
00:08:39,559 --> 00:08:40,720
when we take Zishang back,

170
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:41,840
the people

171
00:08:42,320 --> 00:08:43,840
will be wholeheartedly convinced.

172
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:48,039
Yes, Your Majesty.

173
00:08:59,799 --> 00:09:01,840
Isn't that person Mu Han?

174
00:09:02,240 --> 00:09:03,639
Is something truly going on

175
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:04,919
between them?

176
00:09:22,039 --> 00:09:23,840
I saw you faint in your carriage.

177
00:09:24,399 --> 00:09:26,720
So I had someone
bring you back to my residence.

178
00:09:27,399 --> 00:09:29,240
Princess Fuyu, why not cut to the point?

179
00:09:29,879 --> 00:09:31,559
Why did you use the hypnotic incense

180
00:09:31,919 --> 00:09:33,039
to get me here?

181
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:35,480
If I am away for too long,

182
00:09:35,799 --> 00:09:37,056
the Princess Royal will doubt.

183
00:09:37,491 --> 00:09:38,912
(Princess Royal's Mansion)

184
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:43,080
Mu Han has gone
to Princess Fuyu's place.

185
00:09:43,799 --> 00:09:45,679
Wen Fuyu's place?

186
00:09:47,399 --> 00:09:48,000
Alright.

187
00:09:48,639 --> 00:09:49,919
I'd like to see

188
00:09:50,320 --> 00:09:51,799
what reason he has.

189
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:56,399
Then I'll get to the point.

190
00:09:57,799 --> 00:09:59,039
I need you

191
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:00,000
to help me.

192
00:10:01,440 --> 00:10:02,799
My father is old.

193
00:10:03,840 --> 00:10:05,679
When the day that he abdicates comes,

194
00:10:05,919 --> 00:10:08,080
it will be the time
to vie for the throne.

195
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:11,879
So you

196
00:10:12,600 --> 00:10:14,679
want me to help you kill Wen Yanshu?

197
00:10:15,679 --> 00:10:16,360
I want more.

198
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:19,519
I want her dead

199
00:10:20,679 --> 00:10:22,840
and to suffer every possible torment

200
00:10:23,519 --> 00:10:25,000
and die a miserable death.

201
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:27,879
What Wen Yanshu can do,

202
00:10:28,679 --> 00:10:30,240
I can do just as well.

203
00:10:33,039 --> 00:10:35,200
I just disdain doing it for others.

204
00:10:37,279 --> 00:10:39,559
What I've always liked

205
00:10:40,120 --> 00:10:41,399
has always been

206
00:10:41,440 --> 00:10:43,000
what Wen Yanshu holds in her hands.

207
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:44,039
Whatever she loves,

208
00:10:44,720 --> 00:10:46,519
I must take it.

209
00:10:47,320 --> 00:10:48,840
I want her

210
00:10:49,200 --> 00:10:51,039
to suffer endless betrayal
and humiliation

211
00:10:51,480 --> 00:10:53,200
before going mad and dying.

212
00:10:53,679 --> 00:10:55,240
Princess Fuyu, aren't you afraid

213
00:10:56,200 --> 00:10:58,120
that I will tell Wen Yanshu all of this?

214
00:10:59,919 --> 00:11:00,799
Mu Han,

215
00:11:01,600 --> 00:11:03,200
I reckon you're a smart person.

216
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:05,679
You should know how to choose.

217
00:11:07,240 --> 00:11:09,840
Even if you chose Wen Yanshu,

218
00:11:10,759 --> 00:11:12,080
to me, you are just another

219
00:11:12,720 --> 00:11:13,679
insignificant life

220
00:11:13,679 --> 00:11:15,799
that I will have to take.

221
00:11:16,212 --> 00:11:19,232
(Princess Royal's Mansion)

222
00:11:26,679 --> 00:11:28,840
What color do you think this is?

223
00:11:32,240 --> 00:11:33,639
Stop swaying.

224
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:36,000
