228
00:11:43,519 --> 00:11:44,799
I'm in a bad mood now.

229
00:11:44,799 --> 00:11:45,440
I want to kill.

230
00:11:45,440 --> 00:11:46,840
You'd better stay away from me.

231
00:11:47,480 --> 00:11:48,759
You ignorant one!

232
00:11:48,799 --> 00:11:50,000
You were cheated on, you know?

233
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:53,039
So noisy.

234
00:11:53,879 --> 00:11:55,519
Zi Mo, get the carriage.

235
00:12:00,200 --> 00:12:01,799
I wanted to tip her off.

236
00:12:01,919 --> 00:12:03,279
She thought I was ill-intended.

237
00:12:03,480 --> 00:12:04,360
Unbelievable.

238
00:12:05,720 --> 00:12:06,759
