241
00:12:20,399 --> 00:12:21,960
What's with all the fuss?

242
00:12:22,080 --> 00:12:23,080
What happened?

243
00:12:26,759 --> 00:12:28,200
My dog is lost.

244
00:12:28,320 --> 00:12:29,519
I come to look for it.

245
